{"tid":1761363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新民主同盟 公民黨 帶頭請手足！","createTime":"2019-11-29T00:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T01:43:57.000Z","uid":74778,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e046f2de12df03c0d4a09208ec962beb691ea82b","tid":1761363,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:59:45.000Z","msg":"【聘請手足】<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅新當選區議員正籌組團隊，手足如有興趣，請將履歷連同要求待遇及作品集(如適用)，電郵到 neodemocrats@gmail.com。<br />\n<br />\n處理申請需時，請大家見諒並耐心等候。 🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n───────<br />\n招聘職位：<br />\n<br />\n【議員助理(全職/兼職)】<br />\n工作範圍：<br />\n-支援辦事處的地區活動 (包括街站、居民會及地區活動)；<br />\n-協助文書工作，個案跟進，物資管理；<br />\n-需戶外工作。<br />\n<br />\n職位要求：<br />\n-良好溝通能力、中英文寫作能力；<br />\n-熟悉電腦操作，能運用 Photoshop 及多媒體製作軟件更佳；<br />\n-個性成熟、負責任、樂於團隊合作。<br />\n<br />\n【Project Basis】<br />\n範圍包括：<br />\n-文宣設計、網頁更新、拍片等<br />\n-工作時間較彈性，詳情面議<br />\n-需提供作品集<br />\n<br />\n因反送中運動而已被捕、檢控或定罪者不拘。<br />\n<br />\n申請人所遞交的資料將會保密，並只作招聘有關職位用途<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBXyHZ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBXyHZ5.jpg&h=795b24f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NeoDemocrats/photos/a.2844275698939841/2844275748939836?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNeoDemocrats%2Fphotos%2Fa.2844275698939841%2F2844275748939836%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=83fd9e27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NeoDemocrats/photos/a.2844275698939841/2844275748939836?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【聘請手足】<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅新當選區議員正籌組團隊，手足如有興趣，請將履歷連同要求待遇及作品集(如適用)，電郵到 recruit@civicparty.hk，郵件內請列明屬意的工作地區：港島區、九龍西、九龍東、新界東及/或新界西。<br />\n<br />\n處理申請需時，請大家見諒並耐心等候。 🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n───────<br />\n招聘職位：<br />\n<br />\n【議員助理(全職/兼職)】<br />\n工作範圍：<br />\n-支援辦事處的地區活動 (包括街站、居民會及地區活動)；<br />\n-協助文書工作，個案跟進，物資管理；<br />\n-需戶外工作。<br />\n<br />\n職位要求：<br />\n-良好溝通能力、中英文寫作能力；<br />\n-熟悉電腦操作，能運用 Photoshop 及多媒體製作軟件更佳；<br />\n-個性成熟、負責任、樂於團隊合作。<br />\n<br />\n【Project Basis】<br />\n範圍包括：<br />\n-文宣設計、網頁更新、拍片等 <br />\n-工作時間較彈性，詳情面議<br />\n-需提供作品集<br />\n<br />\n因反送中運動而已被捕、檢控或定罪者不拘。<br />\n<br />\n申請人所遞交的資料將會保密，並只作招聘有關職位用途<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFiustC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFiustC.jpg&h=bc4d96b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/photos/a.450720993456/10156630262113457?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivicpartyhk%2Fphotos%2Fa.450720993456%2F10156630262113457%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=5d9cff34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/photos/a.450720993456/10156630262113457?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀AI<br />\n<blockquote>「與您同行」<br />\n<br />\n近排香港局勢仍未穩定，較多年青人會擔心出路。 Tecky Academy堅持「有教無類」的宗旨，孕育出一班不同學歷、身份、背景的新一代程式設計師。 Tecky Academy決定將全額資助因社運而被捕的人士報讀「人工智能及程式設計微學位」，希望有助各位於日後留港／外地發展。<br />\n<br />\n*課程內容及參加資格詳情，請WhatsApp ／Inbox我哋<br />\n*保證參加者個人資料絕對保密!<br />\n<br />\n#香港人 #投票日 #記得早d起身去投票 #AI #Programmer  #TeckyAcademy<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmtxLRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmtxLRu.jpg&h=019877b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tecky.io/photos/a.1242620759210318/1553069384832119?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftecky.io%2Fphotos%2Fa.1242620759210318%2F1553069384832119%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=2f3070fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tecky.io/photos/a.1242620759210318/1553069384832119?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好似幾好<br />\n利淨係睇左標題</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a7585a989474d4a797e31905082eca68353c55c3","tid":1761363,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1130 中學生銀髮集會 12.1 中環遊行 尖沙咀遊行 12.8民陣集會</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"002db31b61def953aa9221f6606a6f38719df2e0","tid":1761363,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好人一世平安"},{"pid":"3319c1649a5c6596bfb97c67a12a0b751e46f7bb","tid":1761363,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:05:17.000Z","msg":"send咗email冇人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲屋企就嚟趕我走 所以想搵工自己搬"},{"pid":"d426b78e401def31ba23032874ac998d4b0753c2","tid":1761363,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3319c1649a5c6596bfb97c67a12a0b751e46f7bb","tid":1761363,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:05:17.000Z","msg":"send咗email冇人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲屋企就嚟趕我走 所以想搵工自己搬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:36:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黎明到！好多機構請手足！加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fc1b40268fc6cb1751bd80138ab0121eb06fc1e8","tid":1761363,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f054ccef7a8c051c6e23e35099494b1e8c5f135b","tid":1761363,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac4518da3765276a5d857f45d968bb5aa94b736","tid":1761363,"uid":198773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T12:58